snippet.title: WinterSports #10 - VC4000
snippet.description: This is game #10 for the Interton/SuperPlay console. There are only two simple gamemodes skijumping and slalom. The skijumping has several different dificulties with sidewind forcing you off the slope. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/07/wintersports-10-vc-4000.html
